Package: BTYDplus
Type: Package
Title: Extension of R Package BTYD
Version: 0.1
Date: 2014-05-15
Author: Michael Platzer <michael.platzer@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Michael Platzer <michael.platzer@gmail.com>
Description: Extends the functionality of BTYD package by providing methods for
    parameter estimation and scoring for NBD, G/G/NBD, CBG/NBD and
    CBG/CNBD-k models, as well as MCMC samples for Pareto/NBD,
    Abe's Pareto/NBD variant and Pareto/CNBD.
License: GPL-3
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.1), BTYD, coda, data.table
Suggests: bayesm, mvtnorm
Roxygen: list(wrap = FALSE)
